edia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the talk\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complexion, though, has changed a little, after Lyles finished only second in his semi-final, 0.12seconds behind Letsile Tebogo of Botswana, who qualified fastest for the final.\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9986685107147885, \"rank\": 0.001331845518181823, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9996767129922179, \"rank\": 0.00032339155111889387, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The complexion\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"his semi-final, 0.12seconds\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the one hand, there might be little cause for panic: remember, Lyles did not win either his heat or his semi-final en route to gold in the 100m, consoling himself with the idea that others were expending more than was wise when afforded their one shot at the king.\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9986685107147885, \"rank\": 0.001331845518181823, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"